Nov 2023 22:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/giora-eilands-monstrous-gaza-proposal-is-evil-in-plain-sight/0000018b-f84b-d473-affb-f9eb09af0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-f8ea-dafe-a18f-fbebd49b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 21:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-f8ea-dafe-a18f-fbebd49b0000</guid></item><item><title>新民意调查显示，四分之三的巴勒斯坦人支持哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击。为什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/three-quarters-of-palestinians-support-hamas-attack-on-october-7-says-new-poll-why/0000018b-f841-d473-affb-f9e9eeef0000</link><description>两项新的民意调查提供了对战时巴勒斯坦人心态的深入了解。为了理解研究结果，我们必须考虑受访者的概念世界，他们生活在一个从未自由且总是处于战争状态的社会中</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 19:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/three-quarters-of-palestinians-support-hamas-attack-on-october-7-says-new-poll-why/0000018b-f841-d473-affb-f9e9eeef0000</guid></item><item><title>“比比担心释放人质的政治结果”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/my-estimate-is-that-bibis-afraid-of-the-political-result-of-releasing-the-hostages/0000018b-f7e3-d330-a9bb-fff70c460000</link><description>摩萨德行动前负责人兼囚犯交换特使哈盖·哈达斯认为他知道哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔策划 10 月 7 日大屠杀的原因</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 17:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/my-estimate-is-that-bibis-afraid-of-the-political-result-of-releasing-the-hostages/0000018b-f7e3-d330-a9bb-fff70c460000</guid></item><item><title>四天暂停结束后，美国希望以色列在加沙军事行动中更加克制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/u-s-hoping-israel-uses-more-restraint-in-gaza-military-operations-after-four-day-pause/0000018b-f767-dafe-a18f-f76758480000</link><description>美国国务院谴责以色列本周早些时候对加沙联合国法库拉学校的袭击。尽管拜登总统继续支持以色列消灭哈马斯的目标，但官员们对加沙南部的行动感到担忧</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 16:43:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/u-s-hoping-israel-uses-more-restraint-in-gaza-military-operations-after-four-day-pause/0000018b-f767-dafe-a18f-f76758480000</guid></item><item><title>拜登如何敲定以色列与哈马斯人质协议的幕后花絮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/behind-the-scenes-on-how-biden-hammered-out-the-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018b-f757-d7a8-a9cf-f77f58560000</link><description>自从 10 月 7 日哈马斯从以色列绑架了约 240 人以来，美国、卡塔尔和埃及一直在积极努力达成一项协议，以确保他们获释。一名美国官员透露如何最终达成在未来几天内释放 50 名人质的协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 15:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/behind-the-scenes-on-how-biden-hammered-out-the-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018b-f757-d7a8-a9cf-f77f58560000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最大的悲剧即将重演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-biggest-tragedy-is-about-to-be-retold-in-miniature/0000018b-f6dd-dafe-a18f-f7dd87d20000</link><description>“06:30”将通过微缩布景和 10 名幸存者的证词重现 10 月 7 日以色列南部哈马斯大屠杀的恐怖</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 14:16:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-biggest-tragedy-is-about-to-be-retold-in-miniature/0000018b-f6dd-dafe-a18f-f7dd87d20000</guid></item><item><title>针对哈马斯的性暴力证据越来越多，但通往法庭的道路仍然漫长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sexual-assault-evidence-against-hamas-is-mounting-but-the-road-to-court-is-still-long/0000018b-f6bb-dafe-a18f-f7fb0a570000</link><descri